  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Brand Ambassador",
  "description": "<h2>🌟 Brand Ambassador</h2><p>✨ Enjoy meeting new people and bringing brands to life?<br />At <strong>Vision Organisation</strong>, you’ll be part of exciting on-ground campaigns where you connect with the public, represent well-known brands, and build real-world communication and sales skills — all through hands-on experience.</p><h2>💼 What You’ll Be Doing</h2><p>🤝 Represent client brands through friendly, professional face-to-face interactions<br />📣 Share brand messages clearly and confidently at events and campaigns<br />💬 Create positive, memorable experiences for customers<br />👥 Work closely with your team during roadshows, promotions, and outreach activities<br />📈 Learn practical marketing, sales, and communication skills on the job</p><h2>🚀 What You’ll Get</h2><p>🎓 Full training provided — no prior experience required<br />📊 Performance-based growth with clear development pathways<br />🌍 Opportunities to take part in different campaigns and locations<br />🤝 Ongoing coaching, mentorship, and team support</p><h2>🙌 This Role Is Great For You If You</h2><p>✔️ Enjoy interacting with people<br />✔️ Are open to learning and personal growth<br />✔️ Have a positive, reliable, team-first mindset<br />✔️ Prefer active, on-the-ground work over desk-based roles</p><h2>📩 How to Apply</h2><p>If you’re keen to gain hands-on experience in brand engagement and customer interaction, we’d love to connect.</p><p>📱 <strong>WhatsApp:</strong> 9820 2507</p>",
